 up and threaten the old ways of the Order? Or will something new emerge?  By light of flames the new day dawns, rising up on Phoenix wings, scattering feathers of change.  Feathers of Phoenix Flame is the first book of the adventurous fantasy series, The Midlings Saga. Follow Kieran as he travels to the Academy of Magic where he meets Luri, a Veshtu elf. Together the two must try to solve the puzzle of why Kieran can hear the mysterious voice of Akiri, as well as why strange things keep happening around the young mage. Everything and everyone are not always as they seem, and danger lurks far closer than Kieran ever realized.<\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"2641662103762401617\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'22_book_52581363\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"UN1z6+lMZbvLAZOtLiaF08J/XHXAMsZEfWSZq3BVAPku6FZcuzZnZrKFj25TfzDoOM5Ew9VdDfIu6Td1lTlz9g==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"52581363\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"22_book_52581363\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\